windows-registry
Windows registry
version: 0.6.1
license: MIT OR Apache-2.0
rust-version: 1.82
documentation: https://docs.rs/windows-registry/0.6.1
repository: https://github.com/microsoft/windows-rs
crates.io: https://crates.io/crates/windows-registry/0.6.1
features:
 +default = [std]
  std     = [windows-result/std, windows-strings/std]
